OL,3,CLabour to reform energy regulator to
OL,4,Cgive more protections after bills
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FEnergy bill payers have been promised
OL,8,Fmore protections and better customer
OL,9,Fservice as part of plans to reform the
OL,10,Fregulator Ofgem.
OL,12,FThe watchdog could get new consumer-
OL,13,Ffacing powers including shortening the
OL,14,Feight-week mandatory response time
OL,15,Fwhen people complain to their energy
OL,16,Fsupplier.
OL,18,FCustomers could also get better access
OL,19,Fto automatic compensation when things
OL,20,Fto wrong with their energy bills.
