OL,3,CLabour to reform energy regulator to
OL,4,Cgive more protections after bills
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FMinisters say they want to rebuild
OL,8,Ftrust in the sector after energy price
OL,9,Fspikes in 2022 led to soaring bills
OL,10,Fand caused a swathe of smaller
OL,11,Fsuppliers to go bust.
OL,13,FLarger companies have faced
OL,14,Faccusations of profiteering off the
OL,15,Fsharp increase in wholesale costs
OL,16,Fcaused by Russia's invasion of Ukraine.
OL,18,FEnergy consumers minister Miatta
OL,19,FFahnbulleh said the Government has
OL,20,F"learned from the energy crisis".
