OL,3,CLabour to reform energy regulator to
OL,4,Cgive more protections after bills
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FMs Fahnbulleh said: "We will ensure
OL,8,Fthat working people have access to the
OL,9,Fbest possible support to choose more
OL,10,Faffordable, smarter, clean energy that
OL,11,Fis right for them.
OL,13,F"Energy bills are still too high and
OL,14,Fthat is why we worked with suppliers
OL,15,Fto announce #500 million of additional
OL,16,Fwinter support."
OL,18,FShe said the review of Ofgem would
OL,19,Falso "set it up for the transition to
OL,20,Fnet zero".
