OL,3,CLabour to reform energy regulator to
OL,4,Cgive more protections after bills
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FOfficials said there will be a focus
OL,8,Fon improvements to the bill-paying and
OL,9,Fcomplaints process.
OL,11,FThe review will also look into how
OL,12,FOfgem can address wider issues like
OL,13,Fmaking homes more energy efficient
OL,14,Fwith things like heat pumps and solar
OL,15,Fpanels.
OL,17,FOfgem chief executive Jonathan
OL,18,FBrearley welcomed the review, adding
OL,19,Fthat "a great deal" has changed since
OL,20,Fthe regulator's remit was set out 25
OL,21,Fyears ago.
