OL,3,CLabour to reform energy regulator to
OL,4,Cgive more protections after bills
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FHe said the recent crisis was "an
OL,8,Fimportant reminder to all that
OL,9,Fprotecting consumers must remain the
OL,10,Ffocus no matter what challenges we
OL,11,Fface".
OL,13,F"We have already made significant
OL,14,Freforms to stabilise the market, drive
OL,15,Finvestment in our infrastructure and
OL,16,Fbegin to improve standards, however we
OL,17,Fknow more can be done with more
OL,18,Fpowers."
