OL,3,CLabour to reform energy regulator to
OL,4,Cgive more protections after bills
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FLabour set out sweeping plans for how
OL,8,Fit will decarbonise the grid by 2030
OL,9,Fearlier in December.
OL,11,FThey include measures to speed up
OL,12,Fplanning decisions on clean energy
OL,13,Fprojects and free up the queue for
OL,14,Fprojects to get a connection to the
OL,15,Fgrid, which is currently seeing some
OL,16,Fschemes held up for years.
OL,18,FMinisters want to significantly
OL,19,Fincrease how much home-grown renewable
OL,20,Fenergy the UK uses.
