OL,3,CLabour to reform energy regulator to
OL,4,Cgive more protections after bills
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FIt has been pitched as an attempt to
OL,8,Fcut dependence on foreign gas imports,
OL,9,Fwhich contributed to spike in energy
OL,10,Fprices in 2022.
OL,12,FThe review of Ofgem will also examine
OL,13,Fthe regulator's role in approving new
OL,14,Finfrastructure projects like wind and
OL,15,Fsolar farms, and in bringing down the
OL,16,Fgrid queue.
OL,18,FLabour has faced criticism in recent
OL,19,Fmonths for restricting winter fuel
OL,20,Fpayments to those receiving pension
OL,21,Fcredit.
